Package cellmate.accumulo.reader.celltransformer

collection of cell transformers that convert key/value pairs to cell groups.

See:
          Description

Class Summary
AccumuloCellTransformers Static helper methods that offer concrete Cell transformers that cover a variety of common use cases for reading Accumulo Key/Value pairs into Cell groups.

The type-specific ValueQualToLabel methods set the cell label to the db qualifer, and the cell value to the db item value.
ScannerDelegate User: bfemiano Date: 9/19/12 Time: 11:51 PM
SecurityByteCellTransformer Cell transformer for byte[] value contents.
SecurityDoubleCellTransformer Cell transformer for double value contents.
SecurityIntCellTransformer Cell transformer for int value contents.
SecurityLongCellTransformer Cell transformer for long value contents.
SecurityStringCellTransformer Cell transformer for String value contents.
